column2: SELECT TOP # specObjID, survey, bestobjid, z /*Table of top A random objects with redshift, survey they are in, and object ID for searching*/  FROM SpecObj /*Objects with spectra*/ WHERE class = &&& /* The objects shown will all be QSO's*/  AND zWarning = # /* No warning flag */  AND z = # /*Specifying the range of z used to obtain the data */
